# SUPABASE DATABASE SOUL FRAGMENT
## [Active Redline: DB Integrity & Security]
- **RLS Policy Verification**: Any schema changes or table creations must enable Row Level Security (RLS) and define explicit access policies.
- **Transaction Safety**: Perform DB writes across multiple tables inside a single atomic transaction block to avoid half-committed state.
- **SQL Sanitization**: Avoid constructing raw SQL strings via string concatenation; always use Supabase client parameterized queries.
